<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Data Platform Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-width: 200px;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="{{logo}}" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Your OTP (One-Time Password) for verification is:</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otpCode}}</div>
        <p>Please use this code to complete your verification process. This code will expire in {{expirationTime}}
            minutes.</p>
        <p>If you didn't request this code, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>Thank you,<br>User Data App</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>